OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunny spells but cloud increasing with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain spreading south
OL,8,Ftowards midnight. The rain clears
OL,9,Fthrough the early hours with some long
OL,10,Fclear spells developing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA few early showers possible
OL,13,Facross the Borders, otherwise a dry
OL,14,Fday with variable amounts of cloud and
OL,15,Fsome sunny intervals. Winds becoming
OL,16,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
